    <item>
      <title>挪威财富基金将实物资产与股票部门合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/norway-s-wealth-fund-merges-real-assets-with-equities-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威 1.7 万亿美元的财富基金将从 1 月份开始将其实物资产业务领域与股票业务领域合并，以加强对这两种资产类别的管理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/norway-s-wealth-fund-merges-real-assets-with-equities-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 16:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储调查显示，拒绝率上升，信贷获取难度加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/fed-survey-shows-credit-harder-to-access-rejection-rates-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，美国消费者获得信贷的难度加大，汽车贷款和抵押贷款再融资申请被拒绝的比例达到十多年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/fed-survey-shows-credit-harder-to-access-rejection-rates-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Silver Point 成立 85 亿美元私人信贷基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/silver-point-closes-an-8-5-billion-fund-for-private-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Silver Point Capital 表示，该公司已经完成了一只 85 亿美元的直接贷款基金的募集，该基金将专注于向中型企业提供贷款。就在两个月前，该公司刚刚完成了一只 46 亿美元的信贷基金的募集。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/silver-point-closes-an-8-5-billion-fund-for-private-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古尔斯比认为国库清算集中度存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/goolsbee-sees-concentration-of-treasury-clearing-as-risk-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比表示，近年来，规模达 28 万亿美元的美国国债市场的中央清算变得更加集中。他在芝加哥联邦储备银行主办的金融市场集团秋季会议上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/goolsbee-sees-concentration-of-treasury-clearing-as-risk-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国外长斯塔默在 G20 峰会上就人权问题与习近平对峙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/uk-s-starmer-confronts-xi-on-human-rights-at-g-20-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 周一在巴西举行的二十国集团峰会上与中国国家主席习近平就所谓的侵犯人权行为进行对峙。斯塔默对习近平说：“我很高兴我的外交大臣和王毅外长最近会面，讨论双方关切的问题，包括人权和议会制裁、台湾、南海以及我们在香港的共同利益。”中国官员迅速打断并命令英国记者离开房间。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/uk-s-starmer-confronts-xi-on-human-rights-at-g-20-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:18:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选后美国房屋建筑商信心达到七个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售预期上升且市场对特朗普政府将减轻监管负担感到乐观，美国房屋建筑商的信心在 11 月份升至七个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-seven-month-high-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币从美国大选以来代币最大跌幅中反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在波动的交易中从美国大选以来最大的两天跌幅中恢复过来，这反映了人们对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策议程影响的评估不断转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
